Discover a whole new world of artistic freedom here at @Azulik Uh May. ✨ Come find us in the creative crevices of the Uh May residence and unravel the secrets of this modern paradise.

Treat your senses to the boundless tastes of @junglecuisine.azulik —a sustainable, high-end culinary experience that brings you back to the welcoming arms of Mother Nature.🍃

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure! 
📍 @AZULIK Uh May, Mexico
@roth.azulik @byroth_

Witnessing nature’s wild beauty with @agirlwhoblooms at the NIHI Sumba. 🐎 Watch these graceful and powerful creatures freely roam the shores as you relax from your side of paradise. 🌊 Known as the ‘soul of Sumba’ these horses are residents of the Sandalwood Stables where in-house horse whisperer, Carol Sharpe, tends to their everyday needs for a life well-lived with nature. 🌅 

Would you stay here when you visit Indonesia? 🇮🇩 

📽️ @agirlwhoblooms
📍 @nihi, Indonesia
🎶 Tinlicker, Helsloot -  Because You Move Me

Cherishing these romantic moments with @travelmonster.nl at Paragon 700. ❣️ This boutique stay in Puglia is a wine lover's dream come true! 🍷 Ask the in-house sommelier about their rare selections as you gather around the grand convivial table and learn about the Palazzo’s secrets during your wine tasting sessions. 🍇

Ready for a deep dive into the world of vino? Enroll in one of the four masterclass events for an in-depth look into Puglian and Apulian wines. 🥂 

Are you staying here for your next honeymoon? Tag your loved ones below! 💓 

📸 @travelmonster.nl
📍 @paragon700, Puglia, Italy

Meeting @vincentqueijo where the sky meets the sea here at The Edge Bali. 🌤️ How crazy is this overhanging sky pool? 😮 

Hanging over 162 m above sea level, this is one of the most unique pool situations that we have seen! 💦 Treat yourself to pure unadulterated bliss at this cliffside retreat that ensures top-notch service with its internationally experienced butler team and impeccable food choices by Executive Chef Nyoman Susa. 💯 

What will you be celebrating with your special someone this year? Will you stay here when you get the chance? 💓 

📽️ @vincentqueijo
📍 @theedgebali, Indonesia
🎶 Grover Washington Jr. - Just the Two of Us

node.text:
Basking in these golden pink skies of the Philippines here at Amanpulo. 🌅 Have you been to this side of the 'Pearl of the Orient' before? ✨ 

Situated in the ethereal shores of Pamalican Island, this tropical nirvana boasts powdery white sand beaches and glistening turquoise waters that will draw you in the moment you arrive. 💦 There is never a dull moment in your itinerary as activities like kite surfing (December to March), egg hatching ceremonies of Green and Hawksbill Turtles (March to October), and PADI diving certification courses are available onsite. 🐢 🤿

💡 BH tip: If you’re a fan of boats, ask the staff about the private cruise expeditions and sailing lessons. ⛵ 

📍 @amanpulo, Palawan, Philippines

Falling in love all over again in Italy with @terplanet at the Isola Bella Infinity Suites. ❣️ When are you booking that honeymoon trip to Europe? 🌍

Feeling like modern-day royalty at the Palais Capau in Marrakech! 👑 This 5-star ‘riad’ is situated in the lively streets of the city, near the King Mohamed VI Palace, the Hassan II Palace, and is also a few moments away from the Mamounia. 🏰

Make the most out of your stay when you visit the two traditional restaurants inside the hotel and feast on authentic Moroccan fares like tagine and couscous just before you end your days at the hammam. ♨️ 

Is Morocco also on your travel bucket list for the year? 🇲🇦 

📍 @riadpalaiscalipau, Marrakech, Morocco

Going on a Roman holiday with @lumadeline at the Hotel de la Ville. ❤️ Check out this insane rooftop situation! 😮 

Feel like an instant celebrity in this luxury hotel that includes airport transfers in a Mercedes S-Class car with every booking of personalized experiences around the historical city of Rome. ✨ End your days with panoramic views of the ‘Eternal City’ from the Cielo terrace for a candle-lit dinner under the stars that you won’t forget. 🌠 

Would you stay here when you visit Italy? Who will you bring with you? 🇮🇹 

📽️ @lumadeline
📍 @hoteldelavillerome, Italy
🎶 Dean Martin - On An Evening In Roma

Finding our inner peace within this bohemian paradise at the Casa Las Tortugas. 🌾 This barefoot luxury eutopia is nestled on the private island of Holbox, an idyllic escape of white sand shores and glistening ocean waters. 🌊

Enjoy free yoga classes when you book a stay and get cozy in one of the beachfront rooms as you sip on your favorite cocktail for that much-needed retreat back to nature. 💧 

💡 BH tip: Travelers who may need a wheelchair to get around may find it difficult to get around the hotel property. Call in advance if you need extra assistance. 

📍 @casalastortugas, Holbox, Mexico

Feeling infinitely golden with @nickrstic and @detojan at Cesa del louf. ✨ This chalet gives you panoramic views of the majestic snowcapped peaks of the Dolomites, a UNESCO heritage that is a sight to behold all year long. 🏔️ 

Get your skis ready and hop on the slopes as the hotel gives you direct access to the mountains. ⛷️

Need to recharge? Book your spa treatments and relax your senses at the wellness area that includes a Turkish bath, a sauna, and a swimming pool. 💦 

Have you seen the Dolomites in person? Would you stay here? 🇮🇹 

📽️ @nickrstic and @detojan
📍 @cesa_del_louf, Italy
🎶 Harry Styles - Golden

We’re taking in the magical view at Villa Geba @villagebasvetistefan. 😌 This boutique hotel in Montenegro has the best view of Sveti Stefan island. You can catch the view from almost anywhere you stand in the hotel, from the pool to the restaurant to the suite balconies. 😍

Can you imagine waking up to this horizon?!

📍 @villagebasvetistefan, Sveti Stefan, Montenegro
🎶 HNNY - Sunday

node.text:
Rekindling our relationship with nature here at the @patinamaldives. 🌊 Nestled in the aquamarine shores of the Fari Islands in the Maldives, this peaceful sanctuary offers both seclusion and communal paradise with its vast selection of contemporary accommodations designed by renowned Brazilian architect Marcio Kogan and inviting facilities that are tailor-made for each kind of traveler. 🍃

Watch Mother Earth’s story unfold before your eyes with Patina’s Perpetuality initiative—a passionate approach towards building a more sustainable future. ♻️

💡 BH tip: Patina Maldives offers a free diving lesson for young guests at the island because they believe in educating the future on the importance of marine preservation.

📍 @patinamaldives, Maldives

node.text:
Daydreaming of this luxurious Balinese hideaway at The Young Villas. 🍃 This quiet retreat is in Canggu, just between Batu Balong and Brawa, where you have everything that you need from plush beddings, a private pool, and an inviting poolside outdoor shower. 💦 Be delighted with the well-appointed rooms and curated spaces that are great for those who are looking for IG-worthy nooks and crannies. 👀 

When was your last visit to Indonesia? Share your experience below! 🇮🇩 

📍 @theyoungvillas, Canggu, Indonesia
